        Returns a factory of delegating invocations.

        Note that the specified identifier will be used to detect clashing of invocations (see JRoutineLoader and JRoutineLoaderCompat).

        Type Parameters:
        IN - the input data type.
        OUT - the output data type.
        Parameters:
        routine - the routine used to execute this invocation.
        routineId - the routine identifier.
        invocationMode - the type of routine invocation.
        Returns:
        the factory.
